name: Victorious Jarvan IV
description: Victorious Jarvan IV was awarded to players who reached Gold or higher in the 2011 season. As the first Victorious skin ever released, Jarvan shines in silver armor with a flashy gold trim.

wikiSkinData.distribution: Reward for finishing the ranked season in Gold or higher.
